# 傻瓜也能懂的机器学习 | Foolproof Machine Learning

![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-brightgreen)  
![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.8%2B-blue)

---

## 简介 | About This Project

**零基础机器学习指南，人人都能学会。**  
This is a beginner-friendly, zero-to-one guide to machine learning — no math fear, no coding stress, just real-world examples and hands-on demos.

- **作者 Author**：赖建铭 Jianming Lai  
  Economics Graduate Student, Nanyang Technological University (NTU), Singapore  
  Email: jianming001@e.ntu.edu.sg

